## 9. MCP Connector Interface (Formalized)

```python
class FinanceConnector:
    """Standard interface for all data sources"""
    
    def fetch_raw_data(self) -> List[RawRecord]:
        """Returns raw records from source"""
        pass
    
    def get_source_name(self) -> str:
        pass

# Output contract (all connectors must produce this):
{
    "raw_text": "...",
    "source": "gmail|sms|bank_api",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-05T10:00:00",
    "metadata": {"sender": "...", "subject": "..."}
}
```

Pipeline stays identical regardless of source.

